This Fundamental Rights Impact Assessment (FRIA) is prepared to meet the obligation of EU AI Act **Article 27**, which requires deployers of certain high-risk AI systems placed on the EU market to assess the impact of those systems on the fundamental rights of affected persons before first use.

It is generated automatically from the scanner's detected inventory of AI systems and is intended as a **template** — the deployer must review and complete the assessment for each high-risk system and keep the completed version alongside the other compliance artifacts.

